title: DDFP 282: NFC East & rookie QB preview
itunes:title: DDFP 282: NFC East & rookie QB preview
description:
Shek is joined NFL.com writer Elliot Harrison for a 2014 season preview of the NFC East. How will the Eagles perform under Chip Kelly in year two? Can the Cowboys overcome their defensive issues and who's more likely to bounce back: RGIII or Eli Manning? Plus, which rookie quarterback is in line for the best season: Johnny Manziel, Blake Bortles or ... Logan Thomas? Find out.
